  * #400 add defanged_admin setting to support safe Heroku deployment

  [BUG FIXES]

  * #404 fix using 0 to disable max_deferrals and retry_after
  * #380 port searches should check descr field, not name, for "vlan"

2.039023 - 2018-04-19

