  * Daemons now log to ~/logs/netdisco-{web,daemon}.log
  * Finally wrote the DEVELOPING.pod documentation
  * Removed the MCE workarounds as upstream merged fixes

  [BUG FIXES]

  * Fix sloppy schema calls which broke netmap

